URL: https://github.com/jansteinfeld/tmt
BugReports: https://github.com/jansteinfeld/tmt/issues
Description: The tmt package is developed for the application of the conditional maximum likelihood (CML) estimation in multistage designs (Zwitser & Maris, 2013, <doi:10.1007/s11336-013-9369-6>). Of course, CML-estimation of item parameters for conventional designs is also possible.
